31
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:07,870
Qiao,

32
00:02:08,169 --> 00:02:08,930
ubat ini...

33
00:02:08,949 --> 00:02:09,820
Pernah tak

34
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,120
