35
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,980
Buat apa saya pergi ke bilik awak?

36
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,910
Memang bukan awak.

37
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,960
Dialah orangnya.

38
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,800
Pastinya dia.

39
00:03:49,829 --> 00:03:54,960
[REBIRTH]

40
00:03:55,350 --> 00:03:58,000
[Episod 5]

41
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,160
Saya dah agak awaklah orangnya,

42
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:21,430
Panglima Zhuge.

43
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,390
Seni bela diri dan kebijaksanaan
Panglima Zhuge

44
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:31,680
