59
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,960
Saya ada sebab saya sendiri.

60
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:18,560
Awak tak perlu tahu.

61
00:05:22,910 --> 00:05:23,840
Panglima Zhuge.

62
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,450
Awak ini seorang lelaki dewasa,

63
00:05:30,450 --> 00:05:32,150
