64
00:05:32,150 --> 00:05:33,510
Jika awak mahu saling mengenali dengannya,

65
00:05:33,510 --> 00:05:34,640
pergilah jumpa dia.

66
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:36,600
Dia sedang tunggu awak sekarang.

67
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,800
Jika awak masih nak berpura-pura mati,

68
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,750
janganlah asyik bersembunyi.

69
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,120
Sekejap datang jenguk dia,

70
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,980
sekejap lagi datang hantar ubat.

71
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,240
Qiao bukannya bodoh,

72
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:48,409
