awak masih hidup?

73
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:55,310
Awak buat apa?

74
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,000
Apa yang saya cakap tak betul?

75
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,680
Zhuge Yue,

76
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,610
awak nak bunuh saya?

77
00:06:00,290 --> 00:06:01,040
Zhuge Yue,

78
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,680
awak nak buat apa?

79
00:06:09,630 --> 00:06:11,030
Biar saya beritahu awak.

80
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,200
Jika awak bunuh saya,

81
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:14,000
akibatnya sangat serius, tahu?

82
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:26,950
Qiao.

83
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,560
Di mana Zhuge Yue?

84
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:31,480
Di mana dia?

85
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,830
Zhuge Yue?

86
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:34,690
Dia tak datang.

87
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:39,850
Qiao, saya dah beritahu awak.

88
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:41,900
Saya yang suruh Song Cheng
cari ubat ini untuk awak.

89
00:06:41,900 --> 00:06:43,300
Kenapa awak tak percaya?

90
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,990
Saya tahu awaklah orangnya,

91
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,070
Zhuge Yue.

92
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:19,800
Qiao,

93
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,570
saya harap awak sembuh.

94
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,480
Zhuge Yue,

95
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,760
saya pasti akan tunggu sampai awak datang.

96
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,830
Sekarang dah hari keenam.

97
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,190
Qiao,

98
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,800
