99
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:54,800
Saya boleh nampak sedikit cahaya
dan bayangan.

100
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,630
Baguslah!

101
00:07:57,870 --> 00:07:59,120
Selama beberapa hari ini,

102
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,000
