dan pulihkan otot.

106
00:08:04,610 --> 00:08:05,830
Kesan ubat-ubat itu pun sangat baik.

107
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:07,890
Saya rasa dalam setengah bulan lagi,

108
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,310
