120
00:08:51,410 --> 00:08:53,070
Saya tak nak pergi mana-mana.

121
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:54,610
Saya akan tinggal di sini.

122
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,720
Qiao,

123
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:58,720
