138
00:09:23,210 --> 00:09:25,340
Namun, awak tak perlu pujuk saya lagi.

139
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:35,790
Yang Amat Mulia,

140
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:37,360
Yanbei sekarang dalam keadaan bergolak,

141
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,670
