144
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:45,740
Patik risau kita tak boleh tinggal lama
di sini.

145
00:09:45,860 --> 00:09:47,590
Beta faham apa yang awak cakap.

146
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,620
Namun, Qiao enggan ikut beta.

147
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:03,800
Yang Amat Mulia,

148
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:05,240
