150
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:06,860
Song Cheng.

151
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,200
Awak pergi upah beberapa orang lagi.

152
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,080
Nak yang kuat.

153
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,320
Cari juga tali, kayu

154
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:14,170
