155
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,410
Kemenyan pemukau?

156
00:10:15,410 --> 00:10:17,400
Sediakan sekali pedati dan bagasi.

157
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,260
Awal pagi esok,

158
00:10:18,540 --> 00:10:20,870
selepas Qiao gunakan botol Air Api
yang ketujuh,

159
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,930
