164
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:30,670
Pukul sampai pengsan?

165
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:31,880
Itu Panglima Chu.

166
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:32,960
Bolehkah

167
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:34,720
