177
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:54,190
Sediakan juga pedati yang paling besar.

178
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:56,840
Kita ikat dia dengan cara yang baik.

179
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,620
Tunggu apa lagi? Cepatlah pergi!

180
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:01,890
Patik pergi sekarang.

181
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:04,750
Oh ya.

182
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:07,200
Ingat beli kuih kegemaran Qiao.

183
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,550
Jangan biarkan dia lapar dalam perjalanan.

184
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,070
Baik.

185
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,420
Patik akan pergi uruskan sekarang.

186
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:12,570
Beli kuih kegemaran Qiao

187
00:11:13,070 --> 00:11:13,640
