188
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:14,120
Awak...

189
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,160
Biar saya minum sendiri.

190
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,650
Yang Amat Mulia,

191
00:11:34,790 --> 00:11:37,270
Tuan Muda Zhuge Yue telah menghantar
beberapa ubat ke sini,

192
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:39,550
