210
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:10,440
Hantar ubat kepada hamba
macam saya dalam cuaca sejuk begini,

211
00:12:08,190 --> 00:12:09,410
♪ Hujan turun ♪

212
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:11,160
♪ Rinduan yang tertinggal ♪

213
00:12:10,790 --> 00:12:12,200
Tuan Muda Zhuge Yue

214
00:12:11,930 --> 00:12:14,160
♪ Muncul lagi ♪

215
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,860
