216
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,580
Mulut awak tajam betul.

217
00:12:15,650 --> 00:12:17,830
♪ Angin memalsukan ♪

218
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:19,080
Saya rasa awak telah lama sembuh.

219
00:12:18,070 --> 00:12:21,720
