221
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:30,440
♪ Daripada bayangan yang adanya kau ♪

222
00:12:31,060 --> 00:12:34,040
♪ Di sebalik bayangan yang tak nyata ♪

223
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:37,660
♪ Tunggu untuk tenggelam ♪

224
00:12:37,690 --> 00:12:42,110
♪ Hanya memohon kebahagiaan di dunia ♪

225
00:12:42,300 --> 00:12:45,900
♪ Demi satu janji untuk kembali ♪

226
00:12:46,340 --> 00:12:48,340
♪ Masuk ke dalam perangkap sendiri ♪

227
00:12:48,370 --> 00:12:50,080
♪ Menempuh segala kesusahan ♪

228
00:12:50,110 --> 00:12:52,710
♪ Mencari namamu ♪

229
00:12:52,790 --> 00:12:57,510
♪ Sehingga ribut bertiup semula ♪

230
00:12:57,540 --> 00:13:01,420
♪ Tak berbaloi untuk dikesali ♪

231
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:03,440
♪ Cairkan ais ♪

232
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:05,470
♪ Yang terbentuk takdir ♪

233
00:13:05,490 --> 00:13:10,700
♪ Biar malam ♪

234
00:13:12,050 --> 00:13:17,370
♪ Sentiasa terang ♪

235
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:37,100
Siapa awak?

236
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,690
Siapa awak sebenarnya?

237
00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:44,900
Kenapa awak hantar Air Api kepada saya?

238
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:00,120
Qi.

239
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:02,440
Jangan-jangan awak Yue Qi?

240
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,960
Yue Qi, kenapa awak tak bercakap?

241
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:14,440
Awak tercedera di tasik ais

242
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:16,790
